Super hit movie. I strongly recommend people to kindly watch this movie and change their opinion on Akhil. I used to hate Akhil as I thought he is like a pilla bachcha. But after seeing the trailer and his dance movements, I went to watch the movie today, and I was thrilled. The movie would completely take you to a joy ride in all the departments. Songs are highlight, his dance is unbelievable. Believe me he is so energetic on the screen . He is vibrant too. I generally love dancing. And his dance moves are extremely good. Fights in the movie are so confidently executed. The punch he delivers in the fight has confidence. DOP is excellent. He looked very stylish at the same time very cute. The love story is very heart touching. His compassion and acting is found to be very good. Loved the performance of Niddhi Agarwal. She acted like a true love seeker. Comedy is excellent all through out. Comedy delivered by hyper Aadi and priyadarshini will keep you laughing throughout. The "konda" comedy character induced very novelly is a special comedy highlight. Frankly speaking F2 movie had comedy, but no movie can continue sustaining just based on the comedy. 2nd half of F2 could not deliver as per the expectation it has put in the 1st half. But Mr. Majnu had comedy induced in the places where ever it is required. You know the salt and pepper is very much appropriately added in the form of comedy scenes to the required levels. Hence the comedy can be found through out the film in right quantities that helped me not get bored at all. I want to repeat saying that songs are well lyricised and tunes are well composed. The songs will keep Mr. Majnu alive for decades. Big thank you to Thaman In short this is the finest performance given by each and everyone especially Akhil. And  he has proved it. Please do watch. Do not get bowed down by the  past image on Akhil. Kindly encourage such kind of film.
